videos.headline: UNC's Surratt falls over with mysterious injury
videos.description: North Carolina's Chazz Surratt collapses for no clear reason and later walks to the sidelines.

videos.headline: Brown's 52-yard TD increases UNC's lead
videos.description: Sam Howell hits Dyami Brown in stride and he takes it the rest of the way for a 52-yard UNC touchdown.
